title: 152 Plymouth St
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 300322267', 'Rent: $2,795 / Month', 'Beds: 4', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 09/01/2022', 'Pet: No Pets', 'Rent Includes:: Water', 'Parking:: off-street parking', 'Good credit and income required.', 'IF STUDENTS - each applicant is required to have a parent co-signer.', 'AVAILABLE 9/1!', 'Awesome 4BD/1BA located on 2nd floor of beautifully maintained building just MINUTES to BSU and Bridgewater Center.', 'Hardwood floors throughout.', 'Large bedrooms with ample closet space.', 'Additional storage may be available if needed.', 'Cute and spacious eat-in kitchen with large pantry.', 'Large sunny living room.', '4 people max.', '4 off-street parking spots available for rent.', 'NO LAUNDRY ON SITE!', 'The landlords are asking for First, and Security, and we charge a 1/2 month Broker Fee.', 'The Gas and Electric utilities are the tenants responsibility.', 'Water, sewage/trash, snow removal, and landscaping are included in rent.', 'NO PETS, please!', 'Please EMAIL', 'Kaitlin Huyghe, Listing Agent', 'Northeast Realty + Co.', '12 month lease required.', 'The landlord is asking for First, parking, and Security, and we charge a 1/2 month Broker Fee.', 'The Gas and Electric utilities are the tenants responsibility.', 'Sewage/trash, snow removal, and landscaping are included in rent.', 'NO PETS, please!', 'NO LAUNDRY ON SITE!', 'IF STUDENTS - each applicant is required to have a parent co-signer.']
